songs.title: Fuckin Shit
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Sample]
There are statements I made, and when I believed people would listen to me, at least are regards to certain things which are important for us all, but now it makes no difference, but how come your here at all, I mean in my hotel room? I haven't been visited by anyone for a very long time...

[Instrumental]

[Sample]
Is it true you received unidentifiable signals from space?

[Instrumental]
